anti_stick_cosmo_description: The main attribute is physical defense, and the ability to defend
bloom_cosmo_description: Main attributes are cosmo energy defense and HP.
body_care_cosmo_description: The primary attribute is dual physical defense; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.
butterfly_cosmo_description: The main attribute is physical defense, the effect is resistant; the three-piece set increases the speed by 20 points.

crystal_fire_cosmo_description: Main attributes are physical attack and speed; three-piece set bonus grants 100 physical pierce.
dual_def_cosmo_description: Main attributes are physical defense and cosmic defense.
eagle_eye_cosmo_description: The main attributes are cosmic attack and cosmic damages. The combination of three identical cosmos gives a bonus that increases HP by 10%.
fire_drop_cosmo_description: The main attributes are physical attack and crit damage multiplier; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.
flower_ring_cosmo_description: The primary attribute is dual physical defense; the three-piece set adds 20 speed points.
heal_book_cosmo_description: Main attributes are cosmic attack and healing effects.
hummingbird_cosmo_description: The main attributes are cosmo attack and speed. The combination of three identical cosmos gives a bonus that increases cosmic damage by 5%.
jadelight_cosmo_description: Main attributes are HP and speed; 3-piece set increases Status HIT by 15%.
knowing_cosmo_description: Main attributes are HP and Status Res; 3-piece set increases Status Res by 15%.
letter_cosmo_description: Main attributes are Status HIT and Status Res; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.
lotus_cosmo_description: The main attribute is the HP value, the effect hits; the three-piece set increases the speed by 20 points.
new_moon_cosmo_description: Main attributes are defense and speed; 3-piece set increases speed by 20.
p_stone_cosmo_description: Main attributes are physical attack and defense; 3-piece set increases physical attack by10%.
peace_fruit_cosmo_description: The primary attribute is dual cosmic defense; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.
purple_nether_cosmo_description: Main attributes are cosmic pierce and cosmic resist; three piece set bonus grants +10% HP.

seiya_cosmo_description: Main attributes are HP and Status HIT.
spirit_print_cosmo_description: Main attributes are cosmic defense and HP; 3-piece set increases C.DMG Res by 10%.
staunch_cosmo_description: Main attribute is crit; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.
tenacity_cosmo_description: Main attributes are defense and HP; 3-piece set increases HP by 10%.

blood_elf_cosmo_description: When attaking, decreases the target's defense and Cosmo Energy Defense by 10% for 2 rounds
book_of_the_dead_cosmo_description: Grants 20% Physical and Comic Attack when a friendly unit dies (lasts 3 rounds), and recovers 20% HP. Overhealing will be converted into a shield.
chimera_cosmo_description: Increases Physical Attack by 15% and Crit by 4% when attacking manually (lasts 4 rounds). Speed is permanently reduced by 30% after attacking.
daffodil_cosmo_description: Increases physical attack by 1% for every 1% HP lost
decelerator_cosmo_description: When attacking, decrease the target's speed by 30 for 2 rounds
equinox_flower_cosmo_description: Increases attack by 20% and max HP by 10% for summoned units
felina_cosmo_description: If no Energy is consummed in the previous round, increases the damage of the current action round by 50% (not including Assist)
hephaestus__armor_cosmo_description: After taking a critical hit, produces a shield equal to 15% max HP (cannot stack) for 1 round
hyacinth_cosmo_description: When attaking, decreases the target's physical and Cosmo attack by 10% for 2 rounds (stacks up to 5 times)
iris_cosmo_description: All allied units' speed increased by 10
king_giant_cosmo_description: Increases damage by 60% against units below 40% HP
kingfisher_cosmo_description: Critical strikes have a 70% chance to deal true damage (attack x damage multiplier or crit damage, whichever is higher)
manjusaka_cosmo_description: Increases reflect damage by 20% in battle
marsh_fairy_cosmo_description: Gains 1 extra Energy when a round begins (does not stack)
rising_dragon_teeth_cosmo_description: When HP drops below 20% for the first time, applies a 20% HP shield (survive if it is a fatal blow)
roc_cosmo_description: When attaking, 50% chance to gain 1 extra energy
rock_colossus_cosmo_description: Gives you a shield at the start of the battle. Each point of Defense grants you 5 shield. Also increases you P.DMG and C.DMG Res by 25% for 1 round.
salamander_cosmo_description: Increases Cosmo attack by 50% (can stack) in the next action round after killing the target (excluding summoned units)
silver_dragon_cosmo_description: Eack attack has a 25% chance to inflict additional damage equal to 4% of the target's max HP (up to 110% x attack)
soapberry_cosmo_description: After action, recovers 20% HP if below 45% HP
the_sword_of_damocles_cosmo_description: Manually using a skill reduces initial Max Health by 24% and each energy spent (for a maximum of 4) increases P.ATK by 20% and P.Crit level by 200 (for main target).
two_horned_snake_cosmo_description: Deal an extra 40% damage against Saints that have already acted this round.
vulcain_chain_cosmo_description: Increases damage by 40% against units above 70% HP
water_curtain_cosmo_description: When crowd controlled while at below 50% HP, skip to the next round and get an extra move.
wind_elf_cosmo_description: Increases Cosmo Damage Multiplier by 10% during combat. When dealing damage to non-summoned units, this effect is increased by 4% (Lasts 3 rounds).
windflower_cosmo_description: When attaking, decreases the target's Status HIT by 20% for 2 rounds
cosmos_subattributes_priorities_data_0_2: Crit level as important for crit character
cosmos_subattributes_priorities_data_2_2: HP flat > HP % for C characters (< 11k base HP)
cosmos_subattributes_priorities_data_3_1: Speed is the top PVP stat. Status Res is also quite important.
cosmos_subattributes_priorities_data_5_1: Very important for each character with control (freeze, stun, silence, etc.)
cosmos_subattributes_priorities_data_6_1: Very import to sustain (only for DPS)
